title: [Blues] Superharps II - [2001] Carey Bell, Lazy Lester, Raful Ne
description:
Superharps II - Carey Bell, Lazy Lester, Raful Neal and Snooky Pryor (FLAC)
Release Date: 2001


Review:
After the success of 'Superharps' recorded in '99, this is a natural successor. The spot's on the more traditional side, this time. Most of the players here have been around for fifty years - and more, in the case of Snooky. No surprises, solid stuff with a couple of duets, and 'Harp To Harp' which features all four artists. Harp fans will like it.


Tracklist:
1. Walking Thru the Park (Carey Bell)
2. Keyhole In Your Door (Pryor, Bell 2nd solo)
3. I Miss You Baby (Raful Neal)
4. Strange Things Happen (Lester, Neal backup)
5. I Made Up My Mind (Lester, Neal backup and last half of 2nd solo)
6. Let Your Hair Down (Snooky Pryor)
7. What My Mama Told Me (Carey Bell)
8. I Hear You Knockin' (Lazy Lester)
9. Shake My Hand (Pryor, Lester 2nd solo)
10. Starlight Diamond (Neal, Lester intro and 2nd solo)
11. She's Nineteen Years Old (Bell, Pryor 1st solo)
12. Blood Stains On The Wall (Lester, Pryor backup)
13. Harp To Harp (Neal 1st solo, Lester 2nd solo, Pryor 3rd solo, Bell 4th solo, Pryor out of harps solo)


Additional Personnel:
Kid Bangham - Electric and acoustic guitars
Anthony Geraci - Piano
David Maxwell - Piano
Michael "Mudcat" Ward - Acoustic bass
Per Hanson - Drums
